e holder’s max HP to grow more after battling.','もたせると　すばやさが　さがるが\nふつうよりも　ポケモンの　ＨＰが\nたかく　そだちやすい。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/power-weight.png'),(53,'Corde Sortie','Escape Rope','あなぬけのヒモ','Une corde longue et solide permettant de sortir\nrapidement d’une grotte ou d’un donjon.\nElle peut être utilisée à volonté.','A long and durable rope. Use it to escape instantly\nfrom locations like caves or dungeons. It can be used\nany number of times.','ながくて　じょうぶな　ヒモ。どうくつや\nダンジョンから　ぬけだすことが　できる。\nなんどでも　つかえる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/escape-rope.png'),(54,'Huile','Ether','ピーピーエイド','Restaure 10 PP d’une capacité sélectionnée.','This medicine can be used to restore 10 PP to a single\nselected move that has been learned by a Pokémon.','ポケモンが　おぼえている\nわざのうち　１つの　ＰＰを\n１０だけ　かいふくする。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/ether.png'),(55,'Poké Poupée','Poké Doll','ピッピにんぎょう','Une poupée qui attire les Pokémon.\nPermet de s’enfuir d’un combat contre\nun Pokémon sauvage.','A doll that attracts the attention of a Pokémon.\nIt guarantees escape from any battle with\nwild Pokémon.','ポケモンの　きを　ひかせる　どうぐ。\nやせいポケモンとの　せんとうから\nぜったいに　にげられる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/poke-doll.png'),(56,'Fossile Griffe','Claw Fossil','ツメのカセキ','Le fossile d’un ancien Pokémon aquatique.\nOn dirait un morceau de griffe.','A fossil from a prehistoric Pokémon that once lived\nin the sea. It appears to be a fragment of a claw.','おおむかし　うみに　すんでいた\nこだい　ポケモンの　カセキ。\nツメの　いちぶ　らしい。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/claw-fossil.png'),(57,'Déf. Spé. +','X Sp. Def','スペシャルガード','Augmente beaucoup la Défense Spéciale pendant\nun combat. L’effet disparaît si le Pokémon est retiré.','An item that sharply boosts the Sp. Def stat of a\nPokémon during a battle. It wears off once the\nPokémon is withdrawn.','せんとうちゅうの　ポケモンの\nとくぼうを　おおきく　あげ