tain species of\nPokémon evolve. The stone has a fiery orange heart.','ある　とくていの　ポケモンを\nしんかさせる　ふしぎな　いし。\nだいだいいろを　している。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/fire-stone.png'),(74,'Fossile Crâne','Skull Fossil','ずがいのカセキ','Le fossile d’un Pokémon préhistorique terrestre.\nOn dirait un morceau de crâne.','A fossil from a prehistoric Pokémon that once lived\non the land. It appears as though it’s part of\na head.','おおむかし　ちじょうで　くらした\nこだい　ポケモンの　カセキ。\nあたまの　いちぶ　らしい。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/skull-fossil.png'),(75,'Flûte Noire','Black Flute','くろいビードロ','Un jouet en forme de flûte en verre noir.\nAugmente les chances de rencontrer des Pokémon\nsauvages puissants là où l’on en joue.','A flute made from black glass. It makes it easier to\nencounter strong Pokémon in the place you use it.','くろいガラスで　できた　ふえ。\nつかった　ばしょで　つよいポケモンと\nそうぐう　しやすくなる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/black-flute.png'),(76,'Fertipousse','Growth Mulch','すくすくこやし','Un engrais à utiliser sur un sol meuble.\nIl n’est cependant pas adapté aux terres de Hoenn\net n’y a aucun effet.','A fertilizer for growing Berries. However, it appears\nto be unsuitable for the soil in the Hoenn region and\nhas no effect.','きのみを　そだてるときの　ひりょう。\nしかし　ホウエンちほうの　つちには\nまるで　なじまないので　こうかが　ない。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/growth-mulch.png'),(77,'Baie Zalis','Chilan Berry','ホズのみ','Tenue, cette Baie affaiblit une attaque ennemie\nde type Normal.','If held by a Pokémon, this Berry will lessen the\ndamage taken from one Normal-type attack.','ポケモンに　もたせると\nノーマル　わざを　うけたとき\nいりょくが　よわまる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/chilan-berry.png'),(78,'Tissu Fauche','Reaper Cloth','れいかいのぬの','Un tissu imprégné d’une énergie spirituelle\nhorriblement puissante. Apprécié d’un certain Pokémon.','A cloth imbued with horrifyingly strong spiritual\nenergy. It’s loved