as fainted. It also fully restores\nthe Pokémon’s max HP.','ひんしに　なった　ポケモン\n１ひきを　げんきに　したうえで\nＨＰを　すべて　かいふくする。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/max-revive.png'),(116,'Baie Qualot','Qualot Berry','タポルのみ','Une Baie qui rend les Pokémon plus amicaux,\nmais baisse leur Défense de base.','A Berry to be consumed by Pokémon. Using it on a\nPokémon makes it more friendly but lowers its\nDefense base points.','ポケモンに　あげると\nとても　なかよく　なりやすくなるが\nぼうぎょの　きそポイントは　さがる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/qualot-berry.png'),(117,'Attaque +','X Attack','プラスパワー','Augmente beaucoup l’Attaque pendant un combat.\nL’effet disparaît si le Pokémon est retiré.','An item that sharply boosts the Attack stat of a\nPokémon during a battle. It wears off once the\nPokémon is withdrawn.','せんとうちゅうの　ポケモンの\nこうげきを　おおきく　あげる　どうぐ。\nひっこめると　もとに　もどる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/x-attack.png'),(118,'Bandeau Muscle','Muscle Band','ちからのハチマキ','Objet à tenir. Un bandeau qui augmente légèrement\nla puissance des capacités physiques.','An item to be held by a Pokémon. This headband\nexudes strength, slightly boosting the power of\nphysical moves.','ちからが　わいてくる　ハチマキ。\nもたせると　ぶつりわざの\nいりょくが　すこし　あがる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/muscle-band.png'),(119,'Défense +','X Defense','ディフェンダー','Augmente beaucoup la Défense pendant un combat.\nL’effet disparaît si le Pokémon est retiré.','An item that sharply boosts the Defense stat of a\nPokémon during a battle. It wears off once the\nPokémon is withdrawn.','せんとうちゅうの　ポケモンの\nぼうぎょを　おおきく　あげる　どうぐ。\nひっこめると　もとに　もどる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/x-defense.png'),(120,'Atq. Spé. +','X Sp. Atk','スペシャルアップ','Augmente beaucoup l’Attaque Spéciale pendant\nun combat. L’effet disparaît si le Pokémon est retiré.','An item that sharply boosts the Sp. Atk stat of a\nPokémon during a battle. It wear