\nholds one, being hit by a supereffective attack will\nrestore its HP.','ポケモンに　もたせると\nこうかばつぐんの　わざを\nうけたとき　ＨＰを　かいふくする。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/enigma-berry.png'),(168,'Lentilscope','Scope Lens','ピントレンズ','Objet à tenir. Une lentille qui augmente le taux\nde critiques du porteur.','An item to be held by a Pokémon. It’s a lens for\nscoping out weak points. It boosts the holder’s\ncritical-hit ratio.','じゃくてんが　みえる　レンズ。\nもたせた　ポケモンの　わざが\nきゅうしょに　あたりやすくなる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/scope-lens.png'),(169,'Pièce Rune','Amulet Coin','おまもりこばん','Objet à tenir. Double l’argent gagné si le porteur\nse joint au combat.','An item to be held by a Pokémon. It doubles any\nprize money received if the holding Pokémon joins\na battle.','もたせた　ポケモンが　いちどでも\nせんとうに　かおを　だすと\nおかねが　２ばい　もらえる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/amulet-coin.png'),(170,'CT52','TM52','わざマシン５２','Le lanceur bondit très haut et plonge sur l’ennemi\nau second tour. Peut aussi le paralyser.','The user bounces up high, then drops on the target\non the second turn. This may also leave the target\nwith paralysis.','そらたかく　とびはねて\n２ターンめに　あいてを　こうげきする。\nまひ　じょうたいに　することが　ある。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/tm-normal.png'),(171,'Mouchoir Soie','Silk Scarf','シルクのスカーフ','Objet à tenir. Un mouchoir somptueux qui augmente\nla puissance des capacités de type Normal.','An item to be held by a Pokémon. It’s a sumptuous\nscarf that boosts the power of Normal-type moves.','はだざわりの　よい　スカーフ。\nもたせると　ノーマルタイプの\nわざの　いりょくが　あがる。','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/silk-scarf.png'),(172,'Bandeau Pouvoir','Power Band','パワーバンド','Objet à tenir. Permet à la Défense Spéciale de\nprogresser plus vite, mais réduit la Vitesse pendant\nle combat.','An item to be held by a Pokémon. It reduces Speed\nbut allows the holder’s Sp. Def stat to grow more\nafter